_model: main-page
---
title: Open-Source and Free Software
---
body:

This website was created in 2001 by Stéphane Galland. It is a place where you could find several open-source software that are written or published by him or the other contributors to Arakhnê.org.

You could also find these contributions through the [Ubuntu packages](./linux/ubuntu) or our [Maven server](./java/maven-repository) dedicated to the development versions of our projects.
